<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.10.3">
<l>nīrārk kaṭalum nilaṉum muḻutuṇṭu</l>
<l>ērā lamiḷan taḷirmēl tuyilentāy</l>
<l>cīrār tiruvēṅ kaṭamā malaimēya</l>
<l>vārā vamutē yaṭiyēṟ karuḷāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Father who sleeps on a tender leaf of a beautiful banyan,</l>
<l>Having consumed all of the land and the water-filled seas,</l>
<l>Never-sating nectar who dwells on the great mountain,</l>
<l>Tiruvēṅkaṭam, full of fame, be gracious to me, your servant!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
